  "detailed_description": "<h1>Video Reviews</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>Maze Dream is a mix of a maze and puzzles. In this game, you control a sheep prince with the power of the cloud and your objective is to reach the end of the level and jump over the fence.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2397880/extras/c41e161a64dfe77912b72c64905c4940.poster.avif?t=1726776520\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2397880/extras/c41e161a64dfe77912b72c64905c4940.webm?t=1726776520\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >JUMP THE FENCE</h2></strong><br>Your objective is to reach the end of each maze and jump over the fence to move on to the next level.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2397880/extras/8deaecbf0d8bc3f6b326394b3d7c07f2.poster.avif?t=1726776520\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2397880/extras/8deaecbf0d8bc3f6b326394b3d7c07f2.webm?t=1726776520\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >LEARN FROM YOUR MISTAKES</h2></strong><br>To err is human, I say sheep... learn from your mistakes and play it again, without life points in the dream world.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2397880/extras/e2a316b84a22cc02542e61cae8d01863.poster.avif?t=1726776520\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2397880/extras/e2a316b84a22cc02542e61cae8d01863.webm?t=1726776520\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MANAGE YOUR POWER CARDS</h2></strong><br>Use your powers to cross the maze, relax and think a little before acting as your resources are limited.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2397880/extras/c6186cf14cbab1cd445d730a74778743.poster.avif?t=1726776520\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2397880/extras/c6186cf14cbab1cd445d730a74778743.webm?t=1726776520\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >USE THE ENVIRONMENT</h2></strong><br>Study and analyze the terrain and how you interact with it, this could be the solution to the puzzle.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2397880/extras/d3b8ec984765b846eae60e966c4f4465.avif?t=1726776520\" width=600 height=250 /></span><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >UNLOCK SECRETS</h2></strong><br>In some levels you will find secrets, a magic letter or a key without a lock, collect what you can to unlock new experiences.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Use all your cards to beat the maze</h2>",
  "about_the_game": "Maze Dream is a mix of a maze and puzzles. In this game, you control a sheep prince with the power of the cloud and your objective is to reach the end of the level and jump over the fence.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2397880/extras/c41e161a64dfe77912b72c64905c4940.poster.avif?t=1726776520\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2397880/extras/c41e161a64dfe77912b72c64905c4940.webm?t=1726776520\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >JUMP THE FENCE</h2></strong><br>Your objective is to reach the end of each maze and jump over the fence to move on to the next level.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2397880/extras/8deaecbf0d8bc3f6b326394b3d7c07f2.poster.avif?t=1726776520\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2397880/extras/8deaecbf0d8bc3f6b326394b3d7c07f2.webm?t=1726776520\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >LEARN FROM YOUR MISTAKES</h2></strong><br>To err is human, I say sheep... learn from your mistakes and play it again, without life points in the dream world.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2397880/extras/e2a316b84a22cc02542e61cae8d01863.poster.avif?t=1726776520\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2397880/extras/e2a316b84a22cc02542e61cae8d01863.webm?t=1726776520\" type=\"video/webm; cod